+//!                               │  Scheduler  │
+//!                               │(task queues)│
+//!                               └─────────────┘
+//! ```
+//!
+//! # Usage
+//!
+//! The runtime's main loop calls [`IoDriver::turn()`] to process I/O events:
+//!
